---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Efe Ertugrul"
	description="We design and ship production systems at the intersection of AI, infrastructure, and scientific research."
	activeNav="home"
>
	<section class="hero">
		<h1>I design and ship production systems at the intersection of AI, infrastructure, and scientific research.</h1>
		<div class="exits">
			<a class="exit" href="/systems">
				<span class="exit-title">Industry Systems</span>
				<span class="exit-meta">Case studies. Constraints. Tradeoffs.</span>
			</a>
			<a class="exit" href="/research">
				<span class="exit-title">Research</span>
				<span class="exit-meta">Metadata, schemas, FAIR pipelines.</span>
			</a>
			<a class="exit" href="/writing">
				<span class="exit-title">Writing</span>
				<span class="exit-meta">Short, opinionated</span>
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="below">
		<ul>
			<li>Own end-to-end systems: architecture → implementation → operations.</li>
			<li>Ship on Kubernetes in cloud environments with reliability and cost constraints.</li>
			<li>Build secure data pipelines and performance-critical backends for scientific workloads at <a href="https://simmunome.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Simmunome</a>.</li>
		</ul>

		<p class="cta">
			I'm Efe Ertugrul. If you want to see how I think, start here → <a href="/writing">Writing</a>
		</p>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.hero {
		display: grid;
		gap: 24px;
	}

	h1 {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111827 0%, #374151 50%, var(--accent-primary) 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
	}

	.exits {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
		gap: 12px;
	}

	.exit {
		display: grid;
		gap: 6px;
		padding: 14px 14px;
		border: 2px solid transparent;
		border-radius: 16px;
		text-decoration: none;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.exit::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		border-radius: 16px;
		padding: 2px;
		background: var(--gradient-1);
		-webkit-mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box, linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
		-webkit-mask-composite: xor;
		mask-composite: exclude;
		opacity: 0;
		transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
	}

	.exit:nth-child(2)::before {
		background: var(--gradient-2);
	}

	.exit:nth-child(3)::before {
		background: var(--gradient-3);
	}

	.exit:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12);
	}

	.exit:hover::before {
		opacity: 1;
	}

	.exit-title {
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--text);
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.exit-meta {
		color: var(--muted);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.exit {
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.below {
		margin-top: 32px;
		padding-top: 18px;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
	}

	.cta {
		margin-top: 12px;
		color: var(--text);
	}

	@media (max-width: 760px) {
		.exits {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
